ive cases. They are Morang, Sunsari, Bara, Mahottari, Dhanusha, Rautahat, Sarlahi, Parsa, Chitwan, Kathmandu, Lalitpur and Rupandehi.\n\nMeanwhile, six districts have been free of infection. They are Solukhumbu, Mustang, Taplejung, Dolpa, Humla and Mugu.\n\nAmong the infected persons, 141 are receiving treatment at ICU and 17 in ventilator support.","title":"1,228 new cases push Nepal\u2019s COVID-19 tally to 42,877 - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/03/124738/","video":[]}
